4Geeks Academy offers a course titled "Become a AI Machine Learning Engineer." The course is designed for individuals with no previous knowledge and aims to kickstart their career as a data scientist. Participants will learn to build their first machine learning models and enter the highest-paying fields in tech. The course duration is 16 weeks, with three classes held weekly. The class size is limited to a maximum of 12 people. Upon completion, participants receive a recognized certificate. The course covers topics such as Python, SQL, Looker, Streamlit, statistics, and various libraries like Pandas and Numpy. Participants will also explore algorithms like Close Neighbors and Decision Trees, and work with supervised and unsupervised learning models. The course provides real-life case studies to develop practical problem-solving skills and emphasizes the use of industry-standard tools. Students will strategize and develop their own AI projects, covering the complete lifecycle from development to deployment and maintenance. The course is suitable for both English and Spanish speakers, with live classes conducted in the language of the respective campus. For more information, visit the website: https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning stop